:"Is Applied before Student visa expiry required?","a":"Critical deadline"},{"q":"Is Studied in UK required duration required?","a":"Studied in UK required duration is typically required."},{"q":"Is Passport valid required?","a":"Passport valid is typically required."},{"q":"Is IHS paid required?","a":"Assess whether IHS paid is satisfied for this case."},{"q":"Is Not previously held Graduate Route required?","a":"Not previously held Graduate Route is typically required."},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"8–12w — In-country application"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"£822 — + IHS"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"95% — ~90% benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"6 — + completion proof"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt & IHS"},{"q":"What if the client has Applied after Student visa expired?","a":"Apply before expiry; track visa end date from day one"},{"q":"Why is Applied after Student visa expired a problem?","a":"Missed in-country application window."},{"q":"What if the client has Degree not eligible?","a":"Verify eligibility at enrolment—not at graduation"},{"q":"Why is Degree not eligible a problem?","a":"Course or institution not eligible for Graduate Route."}]'::jsonb
